    <p>
        Our elastic neck bandanas are designed to slip comfortably over your dog’s head and rest
        around the neck without feeling tight. Use the guide below to choose the best size.
    </p>
</section>

<section class="glass-card">
    <h2>How to Measure</h2>
    <ol class="sizing-steps">
        <li>Measure around the base of your dog’s neck where a collar usually sits.</li>
        <li>Make sure you can fit two fingers comfortably between the tape and your dog’s neck.</li>
        <li>Use that measurement to pick the size below.</li>
    </ol>
</section>

